                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-183-off1027 t18320906-183-crimeloc1029"></join> on the 25th of August, at half-past eleven o'clock; I saw the prisoner near Mr. Adams' shop -Field took this cap from the right-hand side of the shop door, and gave it to Milton - they went about five yards, and I took them and the cap, which Milton dropped, to the station-house.</p>
